INTRO
This repository contains three part:
//test binary that verify fdl2_sign using libsprd_verify
sprd_verify.c
//libsprd_verify interface for hash verifying
sec_boot.c
//algorithm for signature verifying
rsa: legency rsa function that use montgomery for speed which is not supported by aarch64
rsa_sprd: porting from trustfirmware

NOTES
default algorithm is rsa_sprd
if you use rsa, pls modify Android.mk:
'USE_LEGENCY_RSA := true'
